{"tid":2065150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉中國千人計畫 美國國家衛生研究院開除54位學者","createTime":"2020-06-15T10:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T11:52:38.000Z","uid":75656,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"eb1c8bb113311d214d26b8ca37181abb35f5fa76","tid":2065150,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:50:17.000Z","msg":"知名期刊《Science》報導，美國國家衛生研究院(National Institutes of Health，NIH)正進行一項調查發現，有許多科學家未能清楚交代與外國機構的聯繫，甚至私下收取資金，而這些不明資金有超過9成來自一家中國機構，國家衛生研究院因此已經開除54名學者。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，NIH院外研究副主任邁克&middot;勞爾（Michael Lauer）在12日在一場演講中透露這項調查行動的初步結果。這項調查針對87個機構的189位科學家進行審查，結果發現有133位研究人員未向NIH披露外國資助的收入，比例高達七成，另外54%的研究者沒有披露參與外國的人才計劃。<br />\n<br />\n而因為這項調查，至目前為止NIH已取消了77名研究者的補助資格，並有54位獲得NIH研究補助的科學家遭到開除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2068193\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2068193&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7oVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=a021ee8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2068193</a>"},{"pid":"d1ab8e577e1eb20052b65741609007ab52fcfc2c","tid":2065150,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:06:12.000Z","msg":"美奸可恥"},{"pid":"11e56d22498da7fdd6d0b18916b7f9e2ef7058d2","tid":2065150,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb69cf76371bf40f90546a9597aad7b6a94be911","tid":2065150,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/